<p><b>Online images of bookbindings:</b></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.bl.uk/catalogues/bookbindings/Links.aspx" class="external text" title="http://www.bl.uk/catalogues/bookbindings/Links.aspx" rel="nofollow">British Library Database of Bookbindings</a></li>
<li><a href="http://bindings.lib.ua.edu/" class="external text" title="http://bindings.lib.ua.edu/" rel="nofollow">Publishers Bindings Online, 1815-1930: The Art of Books</a></li>
<li><a href="http://repositories.cdlib.org/sio/lib/6/" class="external text" title="http://repositories.cdlib.org/sio/lib/6/" rel="nofollow">Books on the ocean illustrating cloth bookbinding development and design</a></li>
<li><a href="http://digital.lib.uiowa.edu/cdm4/index_binding.php?CISOROOT=/binding" class="external text" title="http://digital.lib.uiowa.edu/cdm4/index_binding.php?CISOROOT=/binding" rel="nofollow">University of Iowa Libraries Bookbinding Models Digital Collection</a></li>
</ul>
<p><b>Other:</b></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.ioba.org/terms.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ioba.org/terms.html" rel="nofollow">IOBA glossary of book terms</a></li>
<li><a href="http://forum.wordreference.com/showthread.php?t=19794" class="external text" title="http://forum.wordreference.com/showthread.php?t=19794" rel="nofollow">A discussion of title on spine conventions.</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.niso.org/standards/resources/Z39-78.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.niso.org/standards/resources/Z39-78.pdf" rel="nofollow">ANSI/NISO/LBI Z39.78-2000 Standards for library binding</a></li>
<li><a href="http://groups.ebay.co.uk/clubforum.jspa?forumID=18000006076" class="external text" title="http://groups.ebay.co.uk/clubforum.jspa?forumID=18000006076" rel="nofollow">Bookbinding Forum</a></li>
</ul>
